quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  18,21,aur isi terhan hum ne ( logon ko ) un ( ke haal ) se khabardaar kardiya taakay woh jaanen ke khuda ka wada sacha hai aur yeh ke qayamat ( jis ka wadakiya jata hai ) is mein kuch shak nahi. is waqt log un ke baray mein baahum jhagrnay lagey aur kehnay lagey ke un ( ke ghaar ) par imarat bana do. un ka perwar-digaar un ( ke haal ) se khoob waaqif hai. jo log un ke muamlay mein ghalba rakhtay they woh kehnay lagey ke hum un ( ke ghaar ) par masjid banayen ge
  18,22,( baaz log ) atkal pacho kahin ge ke woh teen they ( aur ) choutha un ka kutta tha. aur ( baaz ) kahin ge ke woh paanch they aur chhata un ka kutta tha. aur ( baaz ) kahin ge ke woh saat they aur aathwan un ka kutta tha. keh do ke mera perwar-digaar hi un ke shumaar se khoob waaqif hai un ko jantay bhi hain to thoray hi log ( jantay hain ) to tum un ( ke muamlay ) mein guftagu nah karna magar sarsari si guftagu. aur nah un ke baray mein un mein kisi se kuch daryaft hi karna
  18,23,aur kisi kaam ki nisbat nah kehna ke mein usay kal kardoon ga
  18,24,magar ( Insha allah keh kar yani agar ) khuda chahay to ( kardoon ga ) aur jab khuda ka naam lena bhool jao to yaad anay par le lau. aur keh do ke umeed hai ke mera perwar-digaar mujhe is se bhi ziyada hadaayat ki baatein betaye
  18,25,aur ashaab kahaf apne ghaar mein no oopar teen so saal rahay
  18,26,keh do ke jitni mddt woh rahay usay khuda hi khoob jaanta hai. isi ko asmano aur zameen ki posheeda baatein ( maloom ) hain. wohkiya khoob dekhnay wala aurkiya khoob suneney wala hai. is ke siwa un ka koi karsaaz nahi aur nah woh apne hukum mein kisi shareek ko karta hai
  18,27,aur apne perwar-digaar ki kitaab jo tumahray paas bhaije jati hai parhte raha karo. is ki baton ko koi badalny wala nahi. aur is ke siwa tum kahin panah ki jagah bhi nahi pao ge
